About this item

  • 4K UltraHD Resolution - Experience incredible detail with 4X the resolution of 1080p Full HDTVs.
  • High Brightness LED Backlight - Enjoy a brilliant picture in any room.
  • Enhanced Color - Enhanced color bringing rich, vibrant images to life.
  • Motion Rate 240 with MEMC Frame Insertion - Combines multiple motion enhancement technologies for best-in-class motion clarity.
  • Fire TV Experience – All your entertainment in one place. Fire TV gives you quick access to live TV, video games, music, and lets you stream over 1 million movies and TV episodes. Subscriptions may apply.
  • HDR PRO+ with Dolby Vision, HDR10+, HDR10, & HLG - Enjoy enhanced contrast, accurate colors and fine details utilizing all the most advanced HDR formats.
  • Auto Game Mode (ALLM) - Automatically enables game mode for the lowest possible input lag and latency for an unmatched gaming performance.
  • Dolby Atmos Audio - Advanced spatial audio processing found in movies, TV shows, and video games.
  • Enhanced Dialogue Mode - Audio Setting for better clarity and intelligibility in movies, TV shows, and video games.
  • DTS Virtual:X - Advanced audio post-processing for your everyday content offering an immersive 3D sound, all from just your TV speakers.

    Product Description

    TCL S5 Class Smart TVs offer stunning 4K HDR picture quality with four times the resolution of Full HD for enhanced clarity and detail, all wrapped together in an elegant edge-to-edge FullView 360 metal bezel-less design blending seamlessly into any home. The new High Brightness LED backlight produces a brilliant image in any home. HDR PRO+ delivers bright and accurate colors for a lifelike viewing experience with support for Dolby Vision, HDR10+, HDR10, and HLG. In addition, with Motion Rate 240 with MEMC frame insertion, your favorite shows, movies, and sporting events are enhanced for exceptional motion clarity. Game Accelerator 120* VRR provides fast, fluid gameplay without lag. Additionally, Dolby Atmos and DTS Virtual:X are supported, enhancing your audio experience, and enabling virtualized 3D sound using only your TV speakers. An all-new Enhanced Dialogue mode provides better audio clarity for your TV Shows, movies, and video games. TCL S Class TVs are more than just a Smart TV, but a Smart Choice.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    5 out of 5 stars
    Big TV, big value, solid winner!
    It’s big, bad, and beautiful. Why in the world would anyone spend more than this on a TV when this thing is simply amazing. I read every review on Amazon on this TV before I purchased it. Laggy remote and interface, lack of Xfinity apps.. you name it. Does it take a half second from pressing a button on the remote to translate to the TV- yes definitely. The missing Xfinity app- it’s just in the App Store to download just not preinstalled. Easy. TV was delivered fast by two nice guys in a big Amazon truck on a Saturday. They simply asked where should we put it. I didn’t select any kind of installation or unboxing. This thing in the box is gigantic, but me and my 12 year old lifted that big box with ease. No damaged packaging, brand new not a returned unit, not a scratch on the box. The packing on this is great, for those worried about it getting shipped, unless you dropped it off the truck, I would trust delivery. It took longer to unbox simply due to size than hooking up. Had issues with my router blocking the connection to Amazon to update, but once I figured that out TV updated itself then I linked to my account. I also purchased the bundle with the matching TCL 2.1 soundbar and that was plug and play out of the box with this TV. Installed the missing apps that I had on my last Roku TV, hooked up Xbox, which was also automatically detected and plug and play, and done. Color out of the box was perfect for me. The TV with auto switch to the best possible setting for whatever source is feeding it. Some Amazon and Netflix shows were Dolby Atmos, some not. TV sensed that and just adjusted. Clarity and brightness is superb. Xbox games are fluid and colorful as expected. The size is a monster compared to our older 55” TCL Roku TV. Needed a larger stand as the legs are far wider than the 55”. Like I said, I’m not sure why you would need a $2,000 TV, this does ball that at a fraction of the price. Lastly since it’s Fire TV I get things like my Amazon Music app which thumps with the 2.1 soundbar’s subwoofer. You get Alexa- which now my Echo dots around the house can control the TV. Is awesome. Been buying TCL TV’s for years with no issues. We have 3 in the house. I would recommend this to anyone.

    • Stephen
      5.0 out of 5 stars A Compelling Blend of Size, Smart Features, and Affordability
      Reviewed in the United States on February 18, 2025
      Size: 75 inchesStyle: TV onlyVerified Purchase
      There are televisions, and then there are immersive entertainment experiences. The TCL 75-Inch Class S5 UHD 4K LED Smart TV (75S551F, 2024 Model) is not just a screen—it is a window into a world of breathtaking color, cinematic sound, and seamless smart integration.
      Picture Quality That Stands Out

      Clarity, contrast, and color—these are the hallmarks of a great TV. The 4K Ultra HD resolution on this display renders every detail with razor-sharp precision, while the Dolby Vision, HDR10+, HDR10, and HLG formats elevate contrast and color accuracy for a picture that feels alive. Whether you're watching a blockbuster movie or the big game, the TCL S5 Series ensures a premium visual experience.
      A Smart TV That Thinks Ahead

      Why waste time scrolling when you can speak your commands into existence? With Fire TV built-in, you have instant access to Netflix, Prime Video, Disney+, and thousands of other streaming options. But what truly sets this model apart is Alexa integration—just say the word, and your TV obeys. No clunky remotes, no endless scrolling.
      Designed for Gamers, Built for Action

      In the world of gaming, every millisecond counts. That’s why the Game Accelerator 120 feature delivers 120Hz Variable Refresh Rate (VRR) for buttery-smooth motion. Add in Auto Game Mode (ALLM) and you have a TV that reacts as fast as you do, eliminating lag and maximizing performance.
      Audio That Commands Attention

      A great picture is only half the story. Dolby Atmos and DTS Virtual:X create an immersive soundstage that brings explosions, dialogue, and soundtracks to life. For true home theater enthusiasts, a soundbar may still be a wise addition, but the built-in speakers hold their own better than most in this category.
      What You Need to Know

      Let’s be clear—at this price, you are not getting OLED. Viewing angles could be wider, and for those who crave deeper blacks, the lack of local dimming may leave something to be desired. But in its class, the S5 delivers exceptional value—competing with TVs twice its price and leaving budget competitors in the dust.
      The Final Word: A Must-Have for Value Seekers

      If you’re looking for a massive, high-performance 4K TV with smart features, fast gaming response, and brilliant visuals—this is the one to buy. The TCL 75-Inch S5 UHD 4K LED Smart TV is a powerhouse of entertainment, designed to impress without breaking the bank.

      Order today, and elevate your home entertainment experience to the next level.
